Introduction

Seon Ye In, also known as Sunyoul, is a South Korean singer. He debuted in September 10, 2015 as the main vocalist of the boy group UP10TION under TOP Media.

On December 4, 2023 Sunyoul took to social media to announce that he was picked up by Redstart ENM and would be working with them.
